data.name: StoreDescription
data.value:
He kaiwhakahaere papatopenga a MonkeyPaste, he utauta aunoatanga me te hua pēnei i tētahi atu. Mā te whakarite i tō papatopenga ki tētahi wāhi nui, whakaritea hoki o tō whiwhinga mahi, e whakaatu ana i tētahi atanga kōtaha, iti hoki - kōtaha e tautoko ana i ngā kuputuhi, ngā kōnae me ngā atahanga. I hoahoatia mō te ngāwari ake, me tētahi hapori tipu ake - i aia te taupoki o ngā monomai.
I tīmata hei whakamātautau a tētahi kaiwhakahaere e hiahia ana kia neke atu i te tārua noa iho me te whakapiri i waho o te papatopenga. I pīrangi a ia ki tētahi tono ngāwari pēnei i Ctrl+C ka 'tāpiri kē' o te 'wāhi' he aha i runga i te papatopenga. A, i mahi te whakamātautau. He tino whai take te utauta iti. Na tēnei i whakararuraru te kaihōtaka ki ētahi atu whakaaro me ētahi atu whakamātautau, arā Kua noho ināianei ko "MonkeyPaste".
I te mea kei ō kōnae te papamahi, ko te tikanga kia noho a MonkeyPaste ki tō papatopenga. I āta hangaia ōna huinga utauta ki te whakauru me te whakakotahi ki he taupānga, hōputu ihirangi rānei. He nui ake te Ctrl+C me te Ctrl+V i ngā pokatata noa iho. Ko rātou ngā tauranga o te tāurunga o ngā taupānga katoa tiritiri, e mau ana i tētahi Ko te rawa o te uara me te tikanga e tika ana kia wātea koe i ō matimati. Kāore i makaia noatia i muri i te Ctrl+C panuku.
Ko ahau tērā kaiwhakahaere i kōrerotia i mua, ā, e hiahia ana ahau kia kitea e te katoa te whakamahinga i roto i MonkeyPaste. Nā reira me ōna āhuahira katoa e wātea ana ki te whakamahi. E hiahia ana hoki ahau kia rongo koe i te pai ki te whakamahi. Nā reira ka whakaū atu ahau ki a koe, he tōpana anake i muri i tōna hanganga, ko te NONE o ngā mōhiohio whaiaro (tino) ka puta ake Kua aroturukitia tō papatopenga, kua penapenatia rānei te ANYWHERE ki tua atu i tō ake mīhini. Wā.
